parameters:
Explorer Armada: This is the space created by the followers
of the demon of regeneration, Jien, where they last arrived.

Explorer Armada: I can't believe it... Am I dreaming for
such a long time?

Mage Relm: It's not a dream! This genius mind of mine has
the same scenery burned into it, you know!

Explorer Armada: Hehe, thank you. This is no longer just my
dream.

Explorer Armada: No matter what happens, I want everyone to
come to the back of the room with the door!
Clea: Yes, please let me join you.
